                        <interp inst="t18650410-406-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted at Marl<lb></lb>borough-street Police-court, in November, 1862; to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
